descriptionPlain:
Sorry to disappoint, but this Carl Sagan won&rsquo;t send you into the cosmos. Rather, this Sagan is an easy, relaxing cross between Pre-98 Bubba Kush and Bogs Blue Moon Rocks. Named for the late Carl Sagan, Professor of Astronomy and Space Sciences at Cornell University, this strain pays homage to a great astronomer, intellectual, and cannabis activist.&nbsp;

Though this hybrid is sativa-dominant, it provides consumers with a very well-balanced buzz. Sagan is great for anyone looking for a strain that&rsquo;s strong but not overwhelming. This strain also features a tropical aroma, with lingering tastes of guava and passion fruit.

&nbsp;

